Abuja – Shan George is recovering after undergoing an expensive and delicate back surgery which threatened her life. Nollywood actress, Shan George stepped out for the first time after undergoing a successful spine surgery in Abuja.  The actress was excited after iconic actor, Segun Arinze alongside Mercy Johnson and her husband visited her at the hospital. The new video shared shows the moment Shan George stepped out and tried to walk. Her fans have expressed excitement about the progress made by the actress. See more images: Source